      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "\"Welcome to the Global Dynamics Workplace Etiquette Training Module. This section focuses on general interpersonal conduct, emphasizing the importance of respect, boundaries, and professionalism. Respect involves acknowledging and valuing the opinions and contributions of others, fostering a collaborative and inclusive work environment. Boundaries are essential for maintaining personal and professional space, ensuring that everyone feels comfortable and secure in their interactions. Professionalism encompasses a range of behaviors, including punctuality, effective communication, and a commitment to continuous improvement. By adhering to these principles, we can create a positive and productive workplace for all employees.\"",
      "source": "target",
